"""Test convert_to_snake_case variations."""
string_1 = 'CamelCase'
string_2 = 'camelCase'
string_3 = 'Camel_Case'
string_4 = 'snake_case'
self.assertEqual(self.common.convert_to_snake_case(string_1), 'camel_case')
self.assertEqual(self.common.convert_to_snake_case(string_2), 'camel_case')
self.assertEqual(self.common.convert_to_snake_case(string_3), 'camel_case')
self.assertEqual(self.common.convert_to_snake_case(string_4), 'snake_case')
